<subSubSection id="970447678820BE918A707E8697DD05DF" pageId="null" pageNumber="246" type="nomenclature">
<paragraph id="4FF5279310E809175E80E3CE4242658E" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">
<taxonomicName id="7B6C547DCEACC755DCE40487FDBB6BBF" authority="Favrat" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Orobanchaceae" genus="Euphrasia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="246" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="christii">
<pageBreakToken id="C77585EACCEA32D7E90E2A129927702A" pageId="null" pageNumber="246" start="start">Euphrasia</pageBreakToken>
<normalizedToken id="8AA86769DD79D32B2666EC2543FD0A92" originalValue="Chrístii" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">Christii</normalizedToken>
Favrat
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="E51AD0A4D910E02ED34878E55E13A470" pageId="null" pageNumber="246" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="4E2EC70B9F16CE92BC04F67CFE3FAF94" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">Christs Augentrost</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="4B5522BCA62038415AA054389A95DCA8" pageId="null" pageNumber="246" type="description">
<paragraph id="A73A4ACC1B68168E4774DF79FE7B7480" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="43F41F502522506DD5D476DB63CF87B4" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Orobanchaceae" genus="Euphrasia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="246" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="alpina">
<emphasis id="8E38D1C8D885F3211768448115CFFFF3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">E. alpina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 9) durch folgende Merkmale: 3-10 cm hoch; oberste 
<normalizedToken id="AAA21ED7D9E1081487F07E587D8FBEF3" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
meist so breit wie lang, 
<emphasis id="B19816586A23DEC55281C9C0D91DDF11" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">oft nicht oder nur sehr kurz begrannt;</emphasis>
Frucht etwa so lang wie der zur Fruchtzeit nur wenig 
<normalizedToken id="B1546144DA8DCE04788585F627B1D9E6" originalValue="verlängerte" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">verlaengerte</normalizedToken>
Kelch; 
<emphasis id="B91ABF02FC9EE3EE22056F1D0678D16F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">Krone 7</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="E3AF4605295FB8550610C1DB52DD7899" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">13 mm lang, goldgelb</emphasis>
(im Herbarium verbleichend und besonders an der Oberlippe lila erscheinend). - 
<normalizedToken id="328CCDD4E88E998C293E45CC686B203B" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="0E64CAEE156597CC279E6B54B9943DD6" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6CFFCF189BF48793DE99F78B541159B0" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">
<emphasis id="EF7BD3038F4EEFC892998F459A93B214" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">
<pageBreakToken id="C770687165F7FC849B6DD0801F0309CC" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">Zytologische</pageBreakToken>
Angaben.
</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D496F6259F5BFBB239D08FB1118B082F" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">
<emphasis id="37DE295FF23D9D03777E3CB92A194944" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">Standort.</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="8C23DAA7695C2AE5DAB569784B29BCE1" originalValue="Ähnlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">Aehnlich</normalizedToken>
wie 
<taxonomicName id="0FDFBE2280CD3663452EEA545DFA3BC4" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Orobanchaceae" genus="Euphrasia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="246" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="alpina">
<emphasis id="4E8A59C56BBCBC2F8DC50F2511794A05" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">E. alpina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 9), aber nur lockere 
<normalizedToken id="439EE605278F9D43436C014B368ED66E" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in sonnigen Lagen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8447EFFDE6AE61C48F2D69F46D966691" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">
<emphasis id="B857CE08AA5BA1275A4721DBBA3187A0" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">Verbreitung. Grajisch-penninische Pflanze:</emphasis>
Zwischen Val Piora und Val Peccia im Tessin und Simplon, Saastal, Val die Gressoney (genaue Verbreitungsangaben bei Becherer 1952a), Gegend von Cogne (?), Valsavaranche (Landolt in Herb. ETH), Oberhalbstein (Stalla?).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8DFC3A53986416BBB4A4D1EA5BB08C68" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">
<emphasis id="5F41B0F4B69B5E17F7481A9EF9CA98FB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">
Bemerkungen. 
<taxonomicName id="F376816E3B5B8F13456E0E1CCE6ABCDA" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Orobanchaceae" genus="Euphrasia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="246" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="christii">E. Christii</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
unterscheidet sich mit Sicherheit nur durch die gelbe 
<normalizedToken id="21EBDDCC8F847546DE6E873DF6AF64B0" originalValue="Blütenfarbe" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">Bluetenfarbe</normalizedToken>
von 
<taxonomicName id="9EA993A373BEEB3829A12E197E86BCF8" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Orobanchaceae" genus="Euphrasia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="246" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="alpina">
<emphasis id="E51285AD77E3F5B684ECC8CA0B5CB713" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">E. alpina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 9). Eingehendere zytogenetische und 
<normalizedToken id="07986EDE18DF9809A595CD7243E842A8" originalValue="ökologische" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">oekologische</normalizedToken>
Untersuchungen 
<normalizedToken id="26E8F205667AFDE6CA9308C03400F569" originalValue="müssen" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">muessen</normalizedToken>
entscheiden, ob 
<taxonomicName id="763D7B7307BC846A16869270F4F1CB76" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Orobanchaceae" genus="Euphrasia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="246" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="christii">
<emphasis id="FDCB0435D1F75F7D26F237A2D3E0E30A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">E. Christii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sich durch eine Kombination von 
<normalizedToken id="BF5858D0EB9F15546578F8E209221633" originalValue="ökologischen" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">oekologischen</normalizedToken>
und morphologischen Merkmalen von 
<taxonomicName id="7C7E1F99A179CE069F2B3846D4891DB4" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Orobanchaceae" genus="Euphrasia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="246" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="alpina">
<emphasis id="213C7D13A9D08168253BBA167C227853" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">E. alpina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
abtrennen 
<normalizedToken id="C0C0DEEE8EAF619E197DA8B93BDCAA34" originalValue="läßt" pageId="null" pageNumber="246">laesst</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
